<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Fiches de Révision Mathématiques — Bac Blanc</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1a1208;
    --paper: #f8f4ec;
    --cream: #f0e9d6;
    --gold: #c8922a;
    --gold-light: #e8b84b;
    --red: #c0392b;
    --blue: #1a5276;
    --green: #1e6b3c;
    --purple: #5b2c8d;
    --border: #d4c5a0;
    --shadow: rgba(26,18,8,0.12);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
    background: #e8e0d0;
    color: var(--ink);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 48px 40px 40px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      45deg, transparent, transparent 20px,
      rgba(200,146,42,0.04) 20px, rgba(200,146,42,0.04) 21px
    );
  }
  header .kicker {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 60px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.05;
    position: relative;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  header h1 span { color: var(--gold-light); }
  header .subtitle {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(248,244,236,0.6);
    font-style: italic;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    background: var(--ink);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,146,42,0.3);
    padding: 16px 40px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  nav button {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,146,42,0.4);
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(248,244,236,0.7);
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  nav button:hover, nav button.active {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  main { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px 80px; }

  /* ── FICHE ── */
  .fiche {
    display: none;
    animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease;
  }
  .fiche.active { display: block; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  /* ── FICHE HEADER ── */
  .fiche-header {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 36px 40px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    border-left: 6px solid var(--gold);
    position: relative;
  }
  .fiche-number {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .fiche-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .fiche-tags { margin-top: 12px; display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,146,42,0.5);
    color: rgba(248,244,236,0.7);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  .section {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--shadow);
  }
  .section-header {
    padding: 16px 28px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    user-select: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .section-header:hover { background: var(--cream); }
  .section-header.open { border-bottom-color: var(--border); }
  .section-icon {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 15px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .chevron {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gold);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .section-header.open .chevron { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  .section-body {
    padding: 28px;
    display: none;
  }
  .section-body.open { display: block; }

  /* ── COLOR THEMES PER SECTION ── */
  .s-cours .section-icon { background: var(--blue); color: white; }
  .s-cours .section-label { color: var(--blue); }
  .s-methodes .section-icon { background: var(--green); color: white; }
  .s-methodes .section-label { color: var(--green); }
  .s-exercices .section-icon { background: var(--red); color: white; }
  .s-exercices .section-label { color: var(--red); }
  .s-corriges .section-icon { background: var(--purple); color: white; }
  .s-corriges .section-label { color: var(--purple); }
  .s-erreurs .section-icon { background: #c0392b; color: white; }
  .s-erreurs .section-label { color: #c0392b; }
  .s-essential .section-icon { background: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); }
  .s-essential .section-label { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── CONTENT STYLES ── */
  h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 24px 0 12px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }
  h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  h4 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin: 18px 0 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  p { font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #2c2010; }
  ul, ol { padding-left: 22px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  li { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* ── FORMULA BOX ── */
  .formula-box {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    position: relative;
  }
  .formula-box .formula-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .formula-box .math {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #f0e9d6;
  }
  .formula-box .math .highlight { color: var(--gold-light); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ── INLINE MATH ── */
  .m { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 13px; background: rgba(200,146,42,0.1); padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 2px; }

  /* ── METHOD CARD ── */
  .method-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 16px 0;
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .method-card .method-header {
    background: var(--green);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .method-card .method-body { padding: 18px; }
  .method-card .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .method-card .step-num {
    width: 26px; height: 26px;
    background: var(--green);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .method-card .step-text { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; }

  /* ── EXERCISE ── */
  .exercise {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 16px 0;
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .exercise-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    background: var(--red);
    color: white;
  }
  .exercise-num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .difficulty {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .exercise-body { padding: 18px; }
  .sub { font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .sub strong { font-weight: 600; color: var(--red); }

  /* ── CORRIGES ── */
  .corrige {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 16px 0;
    background: #f5f0f8;
  }
  .corrige-header {
    background: var(--purple);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .corrige-body { padding: 18px; display: none; }
  .corrige-body.open { display: block; }
  .corrige-step {
    display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .corrige-step .cs-num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--purple);
    min-width: 28px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .corrige-step .cs-text { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .result {
    background: var(--purple);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* ── ALERT/WARNING BOX ── */
  .alert {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    margin: 14px 0;
    border-left: 4px solid;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .alert.warning { background: #fdf3e3; border-color: var(--gold); }
  .alert.danger { background: #fdecea; border-color: var(--red); }
  .alert.info { background: #eaf4fb; border-color: var(--blue); }
  .alert.success { background: #eafaf1; border-color: var(--green); }
  .alert strong { display: block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .alert.warning strong { color: var(--gold); }
  .alert.danger strong { color: var(--red); }
  .alert.info strong { color: var(--blue); }
  .alert.success strong { color: var(--green); }

  /* ── ESSENTIAL BOX ── */
  .essential-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .essential-item {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 16px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .essential-item .ei-title {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .essential-item p { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(248,244,236,0.85); margin: 0; }

  /* ── TABLE ── */
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 14px 0; font-size: 13.5px; }
  th { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  td { padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  tr:nth-child(even) td { background: var(--cream); }

  /* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--cream); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--gold); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    nav { padding: 12px 16px; gap: 6px; }
    nav button { font-size: 9px; padding: 6px 10px; }
    .fiche-header, .section-body { padding: 20px 18px; }
    .formula-box { padding: 16px 18px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="kicker">Terminale · Bac Blanc · Niveau Exigeant</div>
  <h1>Fiches de Révision<br><span>Mathématiques</span></h1>
  <p class="subtitle">7 chapitres · Cours synthétique · Méthodes · Exercices corrigés</p>
</header>

<nav>
  <button class="active" onclick="showFiche(0)">① Polynômes 2°</button>
  <button onclick="showFiche(1)">② Suites</button>
  <button onclick="showFiche(2)">③ Probas conditionnelles</button>
  <button onclick="showFiche(3)">④ Suites arith./géom.</button>
  <button onclick="showFiche(4)">⑤ Dérivation</button>
  <button onclick="showFiche(5)">⑥ Trigonométrie</button>
  <button onclick="showFiche(6)">⑦ Produit scalaire</button>
</nav>

<main>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- FICHE 1 : POLYNÔMES DU SECOND DEGRÉ                       -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="fiche active" id="fiche-0">
  <div class="fiche-header">
    <div class="fiche-number">FICHE 01 / 07</div>
    <div class="fiche-title">Polynômes du Second Degré</div>
    <div class="fiche-tags">
      <span class="tag">Discriminant</span>
      <span class="tag">Forme canonique</span>
      <span class="tag">Tableau de signes</span>
      <span class="tag">Inéquations</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- COURS -->
  <div class="section s-cours">
    <div class="section-header open" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
      <div class="section-icon">📖</div>
      <div class="section-label">Mini-Cours</div>
      <div class="chevron">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body open">
      <h3>1. Définitions et Formes</h3>
      <p>Tout polynôme du second degré s'écrit <span class="m">f(x) = ax² + bx + c</span> avec <span class="m">a ≠ 0</span>. Il existe trois formes équivalentes :</p>

      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-label">Les 3 formes essentielles</div>
        <div class="math">
          Forme développée : <span class="highlight">f(x) = ax² + bx + c</span><br>
          Forme canonique : <span class="highlight">f(x) = a(x − α)² + β</span><br>
          Forme factorisée : <span class="highlight">f(x) = a(x − x₁)(x − x₂)</span> (si Δ ≥ 0)
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>2. Le Discriminant</h3>
      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-label">Discriminant et racines</div>
        <div class="math">
          Δ = <span class="highlight">b² − 4ac</span><br><br>
          Si Δ > 0 : deux racines réelles x₁ = (−b − √Δ)/2a  et  x₂ = (−b + √Δ)/2a<br>
          Si Δ = 0 : racine double  x₀ = −b / 2a<br>
          Si Δ &lt; 0 : pas de racine réelle
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>3. Forme canonique</h3>
      <p>Le sommet de la parabole est <span class="m">S(α, β)</span> avec :</p>
      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-label">Sommet et forme canonique</div>
        <div class="math">
          α = <span class="highlight">−b / 2a</span>  (abscisse du sommet = axe de symétrie)<br>
          β = <span class="highlight">f(α) = c − b²/4a</span>  (ordonnée du sommet = extremum)<br><br>
          Remarque : β = −Δ/4a
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>4. Signe du trinôme</h3>
      <div class="alert info">
        <strong>Règle fondamentale</strong>
        Si Δ > 0, le trinôme est du <strong>signe de a</strong> à l'extérieur des racines et du signe <strong>opposé à a</strong> entre les racines. Si Δ ≤ 0, le trinôme est du signe de a partout (sauf éventuellement nul).
      </div>

      <h3>5. Relations coefficients–racines</h3>
      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-label">Formules de Viète</div>
        <div class="math">
          x₁ + x₂ = <span class="highlight">−b/a</span><br>
          x₁ × x₂ = <span class="highlight">c/a</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>6. Pièges classiques</h3>
      <div class="alert danger">
        <strong>⚠ Erreurs fréquentes</strong>
        • Oublier que Δ = b² − 4ac et non b² + 4ac.<br>
        • Confondre α (abscisse) et β (ordonnée) du sommet.<br>
        • En inéquation, inverser le sens quand <span class="m">a &lt; 0</span>.<br>
        • Ne pas vérifier que la forme factorisée est valide (Δ ≥ 0).
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- MÉTHODES -->
  <div class="section s-methodes">
    <div class="section-header" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
      <div class="section-icon">⚙️</div>
      <div class="section-label">Méthodes Types</div>
      <div class="chevron">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="method-card">
        <div class="method-header">Méthode 1 — Résoudre f(x) = 0</div>
        <div class="method-body">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-text">Identifier a, b, c dans <span class="m">ax² + bx + c = 0</span>.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-text">Calculer <span class="m">Δ = b² − 4ac</span>.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-text">Conclure selon le signe de Δ (0, 1 ou 2 solutions).</div></div>
          <div class="alert warning"><strong>Exemple</strong> Résoudre 2x² − 5x + 3 = 0.<br>Δ = 25 − 24 = 1 > 0. x₁ = (5−1)/4 = 1, x₂ = (5+1)/4 = 3/2.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="method-card">
        <div class="method-header">Méthode 2 — Passer en forme canonique</div>
        <div class="method-body">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-text">Calculer <span class="m">α = −b/2a</span>.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-text">Calculer <span class="m">β = f(α)</span>.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-text">Écrire <span class="m">f(x) = a(x − α)² + β</span>. Vérifier en développant.</div></div>
          <div class="alert warning"><strong>Exemple</strong> f(x) = 3x² − 6x + 5. α = 1, β = f(1) = 2. Forme canonique : 3(x−1)² + 2.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="method-card">
        <div class="method-header">Méthode 3 — Résoudre une inéquation f(x) > 0</div>
        <div class="method-body">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-text">Calculer Δ et les racines éventuelles.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-text">Dresser le tableau de signes : repérer le signe de a et positionner les racines.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-text">Lire l'ensemble solution sur le tableau.</div></div>
          <div class="alert warning"><strong>Exemple</strong> −x² + 4 > 0 (a = −1 &lt; 0). Racines : −2 et 2. Le trinôme est positif entre les racines, donc S = ]−2 ; 2[.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- EXERCICES -->
  <div class="section s-exercices">
    <div class="section-header" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
      <div class="section-icon">✏️</div>
      <div class="section-label">Exercices Bac Blanc</div>
      <div class="chevron">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">

      <div class="exercise">
        <div class="exercise-header">
          <span class="exercise-num">EXERCICE 1</span>
          <span class="difficulty">⭐ Classique</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exercise-body">
          <p class="sub">Soit <span class="m">f(x) = 2x² − 8x + 6</span>.</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>a)</strong> Calculer le discriminant et les racines de f.</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>b)</strong> Écrire f sous forme canonique.</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>c)</strong> Résoudre l'inéquation f(x) ≤ 0.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="exercise">
        <div class="exercise-header">
          <span class="exercise-num">EXERCICE 2</span>
          <span class="difficulty">⭐⭐ Intermédiaire</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exercise-body">
          <p class="sub">On cherche les valeurs de <span class="m">k ∈ ℝ</span> pour lesquelles l'équation <span class="m">x² − 2kx + k + 6 = 0</span> admet deux racines réelles distinctes.</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>a)</strong> Exprimer Δ en fonction de k.</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>b)</strong> Déterminer les valeurs de k satisfaisant la condition.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

