<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="fiche" id="fiche-5">
  <div class="fiche-header">
    <div class="fiche-number">FICHE 06 / 07</div>
    <div class="fiche-title">Trigonométrie</div>
    <div class="fiche-tags">
      <span class="tag">Cercle trigonométrique</span>
      <span class="tag">Valeurs remarquables</span>
      <span class="tag">Équations trig.</span>
      <span class="tag">Formules d'addition</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section s-cours">
    <div class="section-header open" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
      <div class="section-icon">📖</div>
      <div class="section-label">Mini-Cours</div>
      <div class="chevron">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body open">
      <h3>1. Le cercle trigonométrique</h3>
      <p>Pour tout réel x, le point M(x) = (cos x, sin x) est sur le cercle unité. <span class="m">cos²x + sin²x = 1</span> (identité de Pythagore).</p>

      <h3>2. Valeurs remarquables</h3>
      <table>
        <tr><th>x</th><th>0</th><th>π/6</th><th>π/4</th><th>π/3</th><th>π/2</th><th>π</th></tr>
        <tr><td>cos x</td><td>1</td><td>√3/2</td><td>√2/2</td><td>1/2</td><td>0</td><td>−1</td></tr>
        <tr><td>sin x</td><td>0</td><td>1/2</td><td>√2/2</td><td>√3/2</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr>
        <tr><td>tan x</td><td>0</td><td>1/√3</td><td>1</td><td>√3</td><td>∄</td><td>0</td></tr>
      </table>

      <h3>3. Formules d'addition</h3>
      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-label">À connaître absolument</div>
        <div class="math">
          cos(a+b) = cos a·cos b − sin a·sin b<br>
          cos(a−b) = cos a·cos b + sin a·sin b<br>
          sin(a+b) = sin a·cos b + cos a·sin b<br>
          sin(a−b) = sin a·cos b − cos a·sin b<br><br>
          Cas particulier (a=b) :<br>
          <span class="highlight">cos(2a) = cos²a − sin²a = 2cos²a − 1 = 1 − 2sin²a</span><br>
          <span class="highlight">sin(2a) = 2 sin a·cos a</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>4. Équations fondamentales</h3>
      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-label">Solutions générales</div>
        <div class="math">
          cos x = cos α  ⟺  <span class="highlight">x = α + 2kπ  ou  x = −α + 2kπ</span>  (k ∈ ℤ)<br>
          sin x = sin α  ⟺  <span class="highlight">x = α + 2kπ  ou  x = π−α + 2kπ</span>  (k ∈ ℤ)<br>
          tan x = tan α  ⟺  <span class="highlight">x = α + kπ</span>  (k ∈ ℤ)
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>5. Periodicité et parité</h3>
      <div class="formula-box">
        <div class="formula-label">Propriétés clés</div>
        <div class="math">
          cos : <span class="highlight">paire</span> (cos(−x) = cos x), période 2π<br>
          sin : <span class="highlight">impaire</span> (sin(−x) = −sin x), période 2π<br>
          tan : impaire, période π<br><br>
          cos(π − x) = −cos x    sin(π − x) = sin x<br>
          cos(π/2 − x) = sin x   sin(π/2 − x) = cos x
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section s-methodes">
    <div class="section-header" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
      <div class="section-icon">⚙️</div>
      <div class="section-label">Méthodes Types</div>
      <div class="chevron">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="method-card">
        <div class="method-header">Méthode 1 — Résoudre cos x = k (ou sin x = k)</div>
        <div class="method-body">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-text">Vérifier |k| ≤ 1 (sinon pas de solution).</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-text">Identifier l'angle remarquable α tel que cos α = k (ou sin α = k).</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-text">Écrire les deux familles de solutions + 2kπ.</div></div>
          <div class="alert warning"><strong>Exemple</strong> cos x = 1/2. α = π/3. Solutions : x = π/3 + 2kπ ou x = −π/3 + 2kπ.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="method-card">
        <div class="method-header">Méthode 2 — Linéariser avec les formules double angle</div>
        <div class="method-body">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-text">Identifier la forme à linéariser (cos², sin², sin·cos).</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-text">Appliquer : cos²a = (1+cos2a)/2, sin²a = (1−cos2a)/2, sinacosa = sin(2a)/2.</div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-text">Résoudre l'équation linéarisée.</div></div>
          <div class="alert warning"><strong>Exemple</strong> Résoudre 2cos²x − 1 = 0. cos(2x) = 0. 2x = π/2 + kπ. x = π/4 + kπ/2.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section s-exercices">
    <div class="section-header" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
      <div class="section-icon">✏️</div>
      <div class="section-label">Exercices Bac Blanc</div>
      <div class="chevron">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">

      <div class="exercise">
        <div class="exercise-header"><span class="exercise-num">EXERCICE 1</span><span class="difficulty">⭐ Classique</span></div>
        <div class="exercise-body">
          <p class="sub">Résoudre dans ℝ les équations :</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>a)</strong> sin x = −√2/2</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>b)</strong> cos(2x − π/3) = 1/2</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>c)</strong> tan x = −1</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="exercise">
        <div class="exercise-header"><span class="exercise-num">EXERCICE 2</span><span class="difficulty">⭐⭐ Intermédiaire</span></div>
        <div class="exercise-body">
          <p class="sub"><strong>a)</strong> En utilisant les formules d'addition, calculer exactement cos(π/12) = cos(π/3 − π/4).</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>b)</strong> En déduire sin(π/12).</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>c)</strong> Vérifier votre résultat avec l'identité sin²+cos² = 1.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="exercise">
        <div class="exercise-header"><span class="exercise-num">EXERCICE 3</span><span class="difficulty">⭐⭐⭐ Difficile</span></div>
        <div class="exercise-body">
          <p class="sub">Résoudre sur [0 ; 2π] : <span class="m">sin x + cos x = 1</span>.</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>Méthode suggérée :</strong> Écrire sin x + cos x = √2·cos(x − π/4) (forme R·cos(x − φ)).</p>
          <p class="sub">Vérifier les solutions en les substituant dans l'équation initiale.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="exercise">
        <div class="exercise-header"><span class="exercise-num">EXERCICE 4</span><span class="difficulty">⭐⭐⭐⭐ Très difficile</span></div>
        <div class="exercise-body">
          <p class="sub">Soit l'équation <span class="m">sin(3x) = sin(x)</span>.</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>a)</strong> Écrire les conditions générales (deux familles).</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>b)</strong> Résoudre sur [0 ; π].</p>
          <p class="sub"><strong>c)</strong> Exprimer sin(3x) en utilisant sin(2x+x) et les formules d'addition. Factoriser l'équation obtenue et retrouver les solutions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section s-corriges">
    <div class="section-header" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
      <div class="section-icon">✅</div>
      <div class="section-label">Corrigés Détaillés</div>
      <div class="chevron">▶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="corrige">
        <div class="corrige-header" onclick="toggleCorrige(this)">▶ Corrigé Exercice 1</div>
        <div class="corrige-body">
          <div class="corrige-step"><div class="cs-num">a)</div><div class="cs-text">sin x = −√2/2 = sin(−π/4). Solutions : x = −π/4 + 2kπ ou x = π+π/4 + 2kπ = 5π/4 + 2kπ.</div></div>
          <div class="corrige-step"><div class="cs-num">b)</div><div class="cs-text">cos(2x−π/3) = 1/2 = cos(π/3). Cas 1 : 2x−π/3 = π/3 + 2kπ → x = π/3 + kπ. Cas 2 : 2x−π/3 = −π/3 + 2kπ → x = kπ.</div></div>
          <div class="corrige-step"><div class="cs-num">c)</div><div class="cs-text">tan x = −1 = tan(−π/4). Solutions : x = −π/4 + kπ.</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="corrige">
        <div class="corrige-header" onclick="toggleCorrige(this)">▶ Corrigé Exercice 2</div>
        <div class="corrige-body">
          <div class="corrige-step"><div class="cs-num">a)</div><div class="cs-text">cos(π/12) = cos(π/3 − π/4) = cos(π/3)cos(π/4) + sin(π/3)sin(π/4) = (1/2)(√2/2) + (√3/2)(√2/2) = √2/4 + √6/4 = (√2+√6)/4.</div></div>
          <div class="corrige-step"><div class="cs-num">b)</div><div class="cs-text">sin(π/12) = sin(π/3 − π/4) = sin(π/3)cos(π/4) − cos(π/3)sin(π/4) = (√3/2)(√2/2) − (1/2)(√2/2) = (√6−√2)/4.</div></div>
          <div class="corrige-step"><div class="cs-num">c)</div><div class="cs-text">cos² + sin² = [(√2+√6)² + (√6−√2)²]/16 = [(2+2√12+6)+(6−2√12+2)]/16 = (8+8+4√12−4√12)/16 = 16/16 = 1. ✓</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="corrige">
        <div class="corrige-header" onclick="toggleCorrige(this)">▶ Corrigé Exercice 3</div>
        <div class="corrige-body">
          <div class="corrige-step"><div class="cs-num"></div><div class="cs-text">sin x + cos x = √2(sin x · 1/√2 + cos x · 1/√2) = √2·sin(x + π/4). Équation : √2·sin(x+π/4) = 1, soit sin(x+π/4) = 1/√2 = sin(π/4). Solutions : x+π/4 = π/4 + 2kπ → x = 2kπ, ou x+π/4 = π−π/4 + 2kπ → x = π/2 + 2kπ. Sur [0;2π] : x = 0, x = π/2 (et x = 2π).</div></div>
          <div class="result">✓ Solutions sur [0;2π] : x = 0, x = π/2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section s-erreurs">
    <div class="section-header" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
      <div class="section-icon">🚨</div>
