        <div class="essential-item"><div class="ei-title">Équations</div><p>cos x = cos α → x = ±α + 2kπ. sin x = sin α → x = α + 2kπ ou π−α + 2kπ.</p></div>
        <div class="essential-item"><div class="ei-title">Double angle</div><p>cos(2a) = 2cos²a−1 = 1−2sin²a. sin(2a) = 2sin a·cos a.</p></div>
        <div class="essential-item"><div class="ei-title">Identité</div><p>cos²x + sin²x = 1. Fondamentale pour toute simplification.</p></div>
